A Nigerian man identified as Saheed Hussain is currently battling for his life at the Aminu Kano Teaching Hospital, after allegedly being stabbed by his wife of 7 months, Hanan. It was gathered that the Bayero University, Kano, law student stabbed Saheed, last night and she has since been arrested. What led to the incident is yet to be ascertained, but it was gathered that Hanan drugged her husband before stabbing him. Source